<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Hello,
I've tried to create label like this:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>

<img src="icon.png" alt="icon.png" />
</code></pre>

<p><em>Label code:</em></p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
&lt;?= $this-&gt;formLabel('selectone', '<img src="icon.png" alt="icon.png" />' ) ?&gt;
</code></pre>

<p>And it escapes the output, so it passes img tag as an escaped string instead of tag.</p>

    </div>
