        <p class="metadata">Posted by Matthew Weier O'Phinney (matthew) on 2008-02-13T08:40:12.000+0000</p> 
        <div class="body">
            <p>You can now pass the attrib 'escape'; when set to a value evaluating to false, the label will not be escaped:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
&lt;?= $this-&gt;formLabel('foo', '<b>Some label!</b>', array('escape' =&gt; false)) ?&gt;
</code></pre>

